    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Teudegrimus">Teudelgrimo</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie <name ref="Grimaldus">Grimaldi</name></persName>,
                        homo <placeName ref="#places/507">Pistoriense</placeName>, riceve da
                            <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia
                        Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>,
                        per cartula livellario nomine (…), omnia et in omnibus casis et rebus illis
                        in <placeName ref="#places/2" key="#Comitatus"><rs key="#Comitatus"
                                >comitato</rs> et teriturio Florentino</placeName>, seu et
                            <placeName ref="#places/507" key="#Comitatus"><rs key="#Comitatus"
                                >comitato</rs> et teriturio Pistoriense</placeName>, adque et
                            <placeName ref="#places/506" key="#Comitatus"><rs key="#Comitatus"
                                >comitato</rs> et teriturio Fesolano</placeName>, pertenentes
                        ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/132">Sancti Silvestri</orgName>,
                        sita <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities">foras <rs key="#Cities"
                                >civitate</rs> ista Lucense</placeName>, qui est de suppotestatem
                        ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, tam casis domnicatis quam et massariciis, cum
                        fundamentis vel edeficiis vel universis fabricis suis, seu curtis, ortis,
                        terris, vineis, olivetis, silvis, virgareis, pratis, pascuis (…) omnia (…)
                        quantas in suprascripto comitato et teriturio Florentino et Pistoriense sive
                        Fesolano vel in eorum finibus, ad parte prefate ecclesie Sancti Silvestri
                        est pertinentes (…). Censo (pro omni censum et iustitia): ad pars ipsius
                        ecclesie Sancti Silvestri per singulos annos per omnem mense ianuario (…) ad
                        suprascriptam eccl(esiam) Sancti Silvestri per nos aut per misso nostro
                        vobis aut ad ministerialem vestrum, qui in ipsa ecclesia pro tempore
                        abueritis aut in ipsa ecclesia ponantur, denarii sol(idos) viginti, denarios
                        duodecim per singulos sol(idos) rationatos tantum. (…) Pena: argentum
                        sol(idos) sexsingentos (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Rachifonsus">Rachifonsus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ermefredus">Ermifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Willeradus">Vuillerado</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Osprandus">Osprandi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        filio <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>, <persName
                            ref="#people/146" key="#Witness">Adalfridi</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Giselfredus"
                                >Ghiselfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ermipertus"
                            >Ermiperto</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>MDL, 5/2, n. 963, pp. 594-595; ChLA, 86, n. 5, pp. 26-28</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
